Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.56,0:23:34.89,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}因為邂逅的正是這個使我悸動的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:39.29,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}約好了哦永遠Be with you
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.49,0:00:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行中的媽媽突然回到家中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.75,0:00:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻得知她正在做一份「邪神獵人」的零工
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與我相撞的這孩子說自己正在找人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.78,0:00:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住址呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有戶主的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.25,0:00:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  這家人姓八坂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找的人的名字叫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  八坂賴子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在尋找的人正是我媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但話說回來  為什麼你爸爸會找我媽媽有事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:01:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我沒問詳細的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.62,0:01:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年和蓮太看起來很般配
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子就交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年你就培育新的愛苗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我…慢著！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.82,0:01:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋臂彎中的位置永遠都是屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.82,0:01:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這理由很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.20,0:01:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子  妨礙別人戀情的傢伙會被烏爾塔爾的貓抓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  你才是吧  把蓮太老弟硬配對給真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.68,0:01:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想我會把你當做備胎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們鬧夠了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}就算少年不和蓮太在一起  他也應該與地球人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.75,0:01:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}你好煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.01,0:01:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很…般配嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～我以個人經驗研究了一下真尋媽媽和蓮太爸爸的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼想他們都不可能有關聯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我即將說的一切都只不過是推測
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為蓮太爸爸和真尋媽媽原先是夫婦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs20\shad0\1c000000\3c99FEF6}巧克力煙斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時他們生下了真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人分手之後  蓮太老弟也誕生了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後蓮太爸爸回憶起從前的快樂時光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發覺自己無論如何都無法忘記真尋媽媽  所以想再見她一面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就讓蓮太老弟去尋媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:03:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hell Missionaries!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.50,0:04:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真尋是我哥哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  奈亞子講的話基本上都是胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋如果是哥哥  還真有點不願意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  畢竟我也不是那麼優秀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是…不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋如果是哥哥的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…就不能成為戀人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙沒救了  得趕快做點什麼才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立了立了  Flag立起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(250,65)\1c7A2BE3\3c7A2BE3\shad0\fscx75\bord6}偉大的X的陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(250,65)\1c7A2BE3\3cFFFFFF\shad0\fscx75}偉大的X的陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  這裡就是我家了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是漂亮的房子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}（那就是環保！！）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}（地球馬上就要撐不住了）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位就是真尋的媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:04:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小尋的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我叫蓮太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要從朋友開始做起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您萬萬不可被這可愛的外表給騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和我們一樣也是不折不扣的邪神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮太老弟  稍微過來下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.25,0:05:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先看中真尋的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狡猾  又沒規定先到先得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是妹子更好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒這種事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  老待外面也不是個事兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先進屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以受到招待嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋的房間…好緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮太飄飄然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這些  你還有事找媽媽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:06:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  是什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是何方神聖！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是八坂賴子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈斯塔  你們也盯上這位女士了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會知道我的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝什麼傻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能把這位女士交給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為勝利的一方是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…請問找我有什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您還沒明白自己的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將您籠絡到的陣營  甚至能夠掌握宇宙霸權
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然有時會去打工  當當邪神獵人什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但完全不是什麼大不了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授和研究會裡其他的前輩比我優秀多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說值得尊敬的人的話  應該是爸爸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬要說的話  小尋也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.95,0:07:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是準備裝傻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別相信那種傢伙說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我不去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是為了救我們而不得不犧牲自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就回來  別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下連本人都同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有你們出場的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了奈亞子  把媽媽救回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:07:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes My Lord！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一樣  女王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我讓開  克子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你擋著我殺不了她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打的什麼算盤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦  最愛的真尋將我公主抱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是說蠢話的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來  克子居然會倒戈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝利的將會是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會讓你們跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦…怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請冷靜下來  真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這讓人怎麼冷靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  其實大部分問題都可以用空手道來解決
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好燙好燙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為自己是女子高中生偵探嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是蓮太把那個消除了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.13,0:09:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他姑且是個風之邪神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「姑且」是多餘的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊  蓮太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很努力不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是做這種事的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快點去救媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不能就這樣放著不管
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們來商量對策吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on baby
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是自己家最舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶真好喝～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是真尋的家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}綠茶果然還是要喝玉露茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  茶梗立起來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好兆頭好兆頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:10:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天肯定會有好事發生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙哇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼啊  真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(263,323)\fs20}混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在少女水嫩嫩的肌膚上…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死人了  為什麼還在悠閒地喝茶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說「商量對策」的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}我已經聯繫行星保護機構的上司  現在正幫我們探明克子的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別生氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  蓮太呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才不還在那邊的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是真尋的房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著  蓮太老弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自作主張地在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.28,0:11:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想問問爸爸到底是什麼事  所以打了電話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:12:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他似乎因為工作太忙了  沒說成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人說過這話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.57,0:12:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下就有可能手握宇宙的霸權了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底  母親大人有什麼秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  說不定就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釨元素！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在補充釨元素
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那只是媽媽亂說的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在別人眼裡肯定比托馬森還沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}註：托馬森：指棒球運動員Gary Thomasson\N他曾經創造過一年被三振132次的紀錄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一是厲害得不得了的啥未知元素怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是能顛覆宇宙的強大能量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  釨元素是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋的母親大人通過和真尋碰觸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能產生的迷之營養素
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣  抱著真尋就能產生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  打住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:13:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  還能這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  產生出來的不是迷之營養素  是個孩子也成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子  你給我適可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能不能也生產出真尋元素呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上司嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨  克子已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太得意忘形了  課長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要扣我的有薪假期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你查到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克子一事就交予我處理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也應該是事出有因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在釀成慘劇之前  我會負責…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這說那的  關鍵時刻還是會挺克子的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除掉克子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果  媽媽和克子在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是在宇宙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  在地球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南緯47.9度  西經126.43度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報座標我聽不懂啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  正是拉萊耶樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這次事件的主謀並非犯罪組織
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有克蘇魯株式會社的內部人員才能進入下沉了的拉萊耶樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  綁架犯是那裡的員工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  母親大人是自願同行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能當做綁架事件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋  你打算怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許媽媽是自願的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算說我任性也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無論如何也想帶回媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道你會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:14:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想為真尋盡一份力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了  蓮太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然決定了  就馬上出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真浪漫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得上次我們去拉萊耶的時候是騎大袞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大袞效忠於克蘇魯公司  這次用不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心  瞧好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅弗連卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就決定是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的愛車
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水陸兩用的特殊車輛  涅弗連卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陸地上無論多麼惡劣的路況它也能輕鬆行駛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水上自不用說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在海底也能跑得了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？帥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次我們去拉萊耶的時候為啥不坐這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.73,0:15:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真不懂行啊  真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事初期就入手船隻的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行動範圍不就太廣了嗎  很為難的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中期坐船終章飛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是常識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最恨別人有本事揣著不使
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系安全帶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.32,0:16:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛輪  啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量120%
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動檔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,15)\fs14\shad0\1c000000\3cFFFFFF\bord3}普通車也只能開自動檔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算開自動檔我也能攻略大峽谷和火焰跑道！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深潛者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不會讓我們輕易接近拉萊耶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們來了  奈亞子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜一碟！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我們逃得掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一會  還有一會量就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥量？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算存夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上魂和氣合的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來一發地圖炮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅弗連卡搭載的無限魚雷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是那麼心狠手辣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有哪有  我有留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於我並沒有克蘇魯那邊參與犯罪的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我還是乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有聽到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子  我坐車很容易暈啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你  暈車藥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這啥歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入場曲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.81,0:17:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dagon-a My House
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:17:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BOSS終於要登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有藥  沒水沖服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿特拉克·納茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事  這裡怎麼會有岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這是大袞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  奈亞子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量也空了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼甩掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我下車  我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子  開穩點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到拉萊耶了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧  能看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好樣的  總算能平安到達呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了海德拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋  真尋  真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮太嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子我們還是到達了拉萊耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  我居然還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.76,0:19:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是拜它所賜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被這個救了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像嗆到水了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裡後就沒呼吸過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就給你做了人工呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看起來像女生  但蓮太是男人啊  是男人啊男人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這絕對不算數  不算數嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的理論武裝能行得通嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行得通  沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥  奈亞子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你擔心奈亞子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  總歸有點擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋  你聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一見鍾情是存在的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜…喜歡真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你合體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著  蓮太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都是男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是我喜歡上的人  碰巧也是個男人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次見面我撞上你  被你拉起來時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你溫暖的手掌觸碰到的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就有感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  有這麼一個說法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界的一切以兩千五百萬年為週期運作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.96,0:21:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說  過了這麼久後  一切的一切都會和現在完全一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說  如果過了兩千五百萬年後  你這份心意尚未改變的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我會欣然接納的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拉鉤鉤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.19,0:21:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勾勾手指頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人就喝上一千杯哈利湖的水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}註：哈利與日文中的針同音  哈利湖為哈斯塔棲身之處
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.62,0:21:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  奈亞子的氣味從那邊傳來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.47,0:21:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣味？你憑氣味就能知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有克子的氣味  她似乎和奈亞子在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.76,0:21:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  快走吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.62,0:23:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為擔心我飛奔而來  你太體貼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.73,0:23:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是無奈啊  劇情安排啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.26,0:23:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教師生涯25年
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.44,0:23:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是教師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋你總算害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.38,0:23:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒害羞好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.24,0:23:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話「市場裡的戰爭」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.19,0:23:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.09,0:23:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？合體機器人的段子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.41,0:23:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  被和諧了


